    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it first rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is sparkling clean inside and out. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Come take a look and see for yourself; I promise you won't be disappointed!",
