    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it departed the factory. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no stone chips or swirl marks, while the interior retains its original factory scent and supple, crease-free leather upholstery. Every button, switch, and technological feature functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive service history and original documentation. From the laser-straight body lines to the pristine undercarriage, this is a collector-grade example that offers the same tight, responsive driving experience as a brand-new vehicle.",
      "price": 46500.0,
