    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this absolute beauty. I've babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in pristine, mint condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
